Entries.default: "Here's to the lot of us, stranded on this damn island."
"Did you see the giant? Last thing we needed is monsters like that walking around."
"Those Dawnstars think everything is Eothas' doing. As if he'd trouble himself."
"Do you know the story behind the Kraken's Eye?"
"Guess the governor was right. Supplies are rolling in, and business is good."
"Neketaka's for the stuffed shirts. Here's to Port Maje!"
"I can't believe someone would steal the Kraken's Eye!"
"Poor Thorel. He's been in low spirits since someone swiped that kraken eye of his."
